<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Vault - Confirmar Email</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #2c587f, #c8e0f7);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    .confirm-container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 400px;
      padding: 20px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 10px 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      color: white;
    }

    h2 {
      margin: 10px 0 30px;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #001d4a;
    }

    p {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    input[type="text"] {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background-color: #d4e4f7;
      color: #333;
      font-size: 16px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      text-align: center;
      letter-spacing: 5px;
    }

    button {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 15px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background-color: #001d4a;
      color: white;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: bold;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }

    button:hover {
      background-color: #002c6c;
    }

    .resend {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #001d4a;
    }

    .resend a {
      color: #001d4a;
      text-decoration: underline;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="confirm-container">
    <img src="/logoVault.png" alt="Logo de Vault" width="50">
    <h1>vault</h1>
    <h2>CONFIRMACIÓN DE EMAIL</h2>
    <p>Hemos enviado un PIN de 6 dígitos a tu correo. Ingrésalo a continuación para confirmar tu cuenta.</p>
    <form action="/confirmar-pin" method="POST">
      <input type="text" name="pin" placeholder="------" maxlength="6" required pattern="\d{6}">
      <button type="submit">VALIDAR PIN</button>
    </form>
    <div class="resend">
      ¿No recibiste el código? <a href="/reenviar-pin">Reenviar PIN</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
